## User Management [/api.json-rpc]
 
### user.auth [POST]

+ Request (application/json) application/json
    + Attributes 
    
      + user: external@free.fr (string, required)
      + password: thestudnet (string, required)
      
    + Body
    
        {
            "jsonrpc": "2.0", 
            "method": "user.auth", 
            "params": {
                 "user": "demo", 
                 "password": "demo"
            }, 
            "id": 1
        }
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)
      
    + body
    
         {
             result: {
                 id: 8,
                 token: 886c54419472ea797c12e82b583a262a7,
                 created_date: 2016-07-19 09:28:14,
                 firstname: firstname_external,
                 lastname: lastname_external,
                 email: external@free.fr,
                 expiration_date: null,
                 roles: {
                     7: external
                 },
                 school: {
                     id: 1,
                     name: Morbi Corporation,
                     short_name: turpis,
                     logo: null,
                     background: null
                 }
             },
             id: 1,
             jsonrpc: 2.0
         }
        
